	1.	Legal Calculus = WHY / Field Guide = HOW
	2.	Blueprint: map facts → elements → burdens → admissible evidence
	3.	Builder: generate work product (timelines, exhibits, SUFs, motions, discovery)
	4.	Inspector: audit for gaps (foundation, contradictions, procedure, credibility)
	5.	The living loop: update → interpret → choose strategy → define tasks → build → inspect → repeat